          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Rakesh Thakur"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-12-27",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The administration and faculty both provide excellent assistance. Quite possibly the best high school ever, packed with extracurriculars and other fun stuff. JM International is rooted on the values of independence, initiative, and free choice. Teachers in schools today are highly trained professionals who are fluent in the use of relevant technologies and skilled in the art of managing students' expectations.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "J M International School - Amrapali Dream Valley"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "babita singh"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-09-14",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Among JM International School's numerous strengths are its excellent facilities, dedicated teaching staff, and other supportive personnel. The course content and delivery are both extremely cutting-edge. Additionally, they provide extracurricular activities. They nurture each child and show them how to become a  good individual. What I've experienced up to this point has been truly amazing and humbling. Teachers are encouraging, and lessons are presented in a playful manner.Student participation in extracurricular activities, such as athletics and STEM activities  to  develop students' abilities to think critically is also strongly encouraged by the school. They have a nicely located campus and is surrounded by good societies of noida and greater noida. The transportation also is quick and frequent.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
